  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0da9\u0dca  \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d86\u0dc0\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dca  \u0dc0\u0d9c\u0d9a\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba \u0db6\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dad \u0dba\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dd2\u2019\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"If there is a wave of covid, the opposition must accept the responsibility\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Public Security Minister Retired Rear Admiral Sarath Weerasekera said in Parliament today (17) that if a wave of Covid comes and the country has to be shut down again due to the public rally held by the Samagi Jana Balawegaya, the opposition should take responsibility.",
        "He said that it is very wrong to hold such protests when the health department has not approved it.",
        "He said this during the debate on the second reading of the Appropriation Bill.",
        "Mr. Weerasekera said that the police are not working on the orders of politicians and the police are working on the instructions of the health authorities at this time.",
        "The minister said that it is very wrong to insult the police officers who play a big role and said that there will be no forgiveness for those who damage the self-respect of the police.",
        "He said that the police are doing a very difficult job and fifteen thousand and seven hundred police officers were infected with Covid while fighting against the corona virus and going to stop the protests.",
        "Mr. Sarath Weerasekera also said that 44 police officers have died due to the infection of Covid.",
        "He also stated that if there is even an iota of feeling about the country, they will request the opposition to stop such public rallies and support the government as important politicians for building the country."
      ],
